<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verifikasi Email Anda - Happy Toothy Dental Clinic</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lato:wght@400;700&family=Poppins:wght@600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="auth-page">
    <div class="auth-wrapper">
        <div class="auth-container">
            <div class="auth-header">
                <a href="/">
                    <img src="/assets/images/logo toothy.png" alt="Happy Toothy Logo" class="auth-logo">
                    <span class="site-title-auth">Happy Toothy</span>
                </a>
                <h2>Verifikasi Email Anda</h2>
            </div>
            
            <div class="verification-content">
                <i class="fas fa-envelope-open-text verification-icon"></i>
                
                <% if (typeof message !== 'undefined' && message) { %>
                    <p class="verification-alert-message"><%= message %></p>
                <% } else { %>
                    <p>Terima kasih telah mendaftar di Happy Toothy!</p>
                    <p>Kami telah mengirimkan link verifikasi ke alamat email Anda.</p>
                <% } %>

                <p>Silakan periksa kotak masuk (inbox) atau folder spam/junk email Anda untuk menyelesaikan proses pendaftaran.</p>
                <p class="small-text">Link verifikasi ini mungkin memiliki batas waktu. Jika Anda tidak menerimanya dalam beberapa menit:</p>
                
                <div class="resend-section">
                    <h3>Kirim Ulang Email Verifikasi</h3>
                    <form id="resendVerificationForm" class="auth-form">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="resendEmail">Email Anda</label>
                            <input type="email" id="resendEmail" name="email" required placeholder="Masukkan email yang Anda daftarkan">
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-secondary btn-full-width">Kirim Ulang</button>
                    </form>
                </div>

                <div class="auth-footer-links mt-3">
                    <p>Sudah verifikasi? <a href="/login">Login Sekarang</a></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>